\c 20
\s Izijeziso zokona
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Tshono futhi ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli \add uthi\add*\x + 18.2.\x*: Ngulowo lalowo wabantwana bakoIsrayeli, loba owabezizweni abahlala njengabezizwe koIsrayeli, onikela okwenzalo yakhe kuMoleki, uzabulawa lokubulawa, abantu belizwe bazamkhanda ngamatshe\x + 18.21.\x*.
\v 3 Mina-ke ngizamisa ubuso bami bumelane lalowomuntu\x + 17.10.\x*, ngimqume asuke phakathi kwabantu bakibo, ngoba enikele okwenzalo yakhe kuMoleki\x + 20.5. Eks. 30.33.\x*, ukuze angcolise indlu yami engcwele\x + Hez. 5.11; 23.38,39. Levi 19.30.\x*, eyise ibizo lami elingcwele\x + 18.21.\x*.
\v 4 Uba-ke abantu belizwe befihla lokufihla amehlo abo kulowomuntu nxa enikela okwenzalo yakhe kuMoleki, ukuze bangambulali\x + Dute. 17.2,3,5.\x*,
\v 5 mina ngizamisa ubuso bami bumelane lalowomuntu njalo bumelane losapho lwakhe, ngimqume\x + 20.5. Eks. 30.33.\x* labo bonke abaphinga emva kwakhe, ukuthi baphinge belandela uMoleki, basuke phakathi kwabantu bakibo\x + Eks. 34.15.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Umphefumulo, ophendukela-ke kulabo abalamadlozi lakwabalumbayo ukuphinga ubalandela\x + 19.31.\x*, ngizamisa ubuso bami bumelane lalowomphefumulo\x + 17.10.\x*, ngiwuqume usuke phakathi kwabantu bakibo\x + 20.5. Eks. 30.33.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Ngakho zingcweliseni libe ngcwele, ngoba ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + 19.2; 11.44.\x*.
\v 8 Njalo gcinani izimiso zami, lizenze\x + 18.4.\x*. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* elingcwelisayo\x + Eks. 31.13. Levi 21.8,15,23; 22.2; Hez. 37.28.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Ngoba ngulowo lalowo othuka uyise kumbe unina uzabulawa lokubulawa; uthukile uyise kumbe unina\x + Eks. 21.17.\x*; igazi lakhe liphezu kwakhe\x + 20.11,12,13,16,27. 2 Sam. 1.16. 1 Kho. 2.32,33,37.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Lendoda efeba lomfazi womuntu, efeba lomkamakhelwane wayo, izabulawa lokubulawa, isifebe lesifebekazi\x + 18.20. Dute. 22.22. Joha. 8.4,5.\x*.
\v 11 Lendoda elala lomkayise yembule ubunqunu bukayise; bobabili bazabulawa lokubulawa; igazi labo liphezu kwabo\x + 18.8.\x*.
\v 12 Lendoda elala lomalokazana wayo, bobabili bazabulawa lokubulawa\x + 18.15.\x*; benze ingxube\x + 18.23.\x*; igazi labo liphezu kwabo.
\v 13 Lendoda elala lowesilisa njengokulala lowesifazana, bobabili benze isinengiso; bazabulawa lokubulawa; igazi labo liphezu kwabo\x + 18.22. Dute. 23.17.\x*.
\v 14 Lendoda ethatha umfazi kanye lonina, kuyinkohlakalo. Bazatshiswa ngomlilo, yena labo, ukuze kungabi khona inkohlakalo phakathi kwenu\x + 18.17. Dute. 27.23.\x*.
\v 15 Lendoda elala lenyamazana, izabulawa lokubulawa, futhi lizayibulala inyamazana\x + 18.23. Dute. 27.21.\x*.
\v 16 Lowesifazana osondela lakuyiphi inyamazana ukulala layo, uzabulala owesifazana lenyamazana; bazabulawa lokubulawa; igazi labo liphezu kwabo.
\v 17 Lendoda ethatha udadewabo, indodakazi kayise loba indodakazi kanina, ibone ubunqunu bakhe\x + 18.9. Dute. 27.22.\x*, laye abone ubunqunu bayo, kulihlazo; njalo bazaqunywa emehlweni abantwana babantu bakibo; yembule ubunqunu bukadadewabo; izathwala ububi bayo\x + Zaga 14.34.\x*.
\v 18 Lendoda elala lowesifazana ogulayo, yembule ubunqunu bakhe\x + 18.19; 15.24.\x*, inqunule umthombo wakhe, laye wembule umthombo wegazi lakhe, bobabili bazaqunywa basuke phakathi kwabantu bakibo\x + 12.7.\x*.
\v 19 Njalo ungembuli ubunqunu bukadadewabo kanyoko, loba obukadadewabo kayihlo\x + 18.12,13.\x*; ngoba wembule isihlobo sakhe; bazathwala ububi babo\x + 18.6.\x*.
\v 20 Lendoda elala lomkamfowabo kayise, yembule ubunqunu bomfowabo kayise; bazathwala isono sabo; bafe bengelabantwana\x + 18.14.\x*.
\v 21 Lendoda ethatha umkamfowabo, kuyikungcola; yembule ubunqunu bukamfowabo; bazakuba ngabangelabantwana\x + 18.16.\x*.
\v 22 Ngakho gcinani zonke izimiso zami lezehlulelo zonke zami, lizenze\x + 18.4.\x*, ukuze ilizwe engililetha kulo ukuhlala kulo lingalihlanzi\x + 18.25,28.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Njalo lingahambi ngezimiso zesizwe engisixotshayo phambi kwenu\x + 18.3.\x*; ngoba benze zonke lezizinto; ngakho nganengwa yibo\x + 18.27. Dute. 9.5.\x*.
\v 24 Kodwa ngathi kini: Lizakudla ilifa lelizwe labo; mina ngizalinika ukuthi lidle ilifa lalo\x + Eks. 3.17; 6.8.\x*, ilizwe eligeleza uchago loluju. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + Eks. 3.8.\x*, olehlukanise labezizwe\x + 20.26. 1 Kho. 8.53; Eks. 19.5; 33.16.\x*.
\v 25 Ngakho yehlukanisani phakathi kwenyamazana ezihlambulukileyo lezingahlambulukanga, laphakathi kwezinyoni ezingahlambulukanga lezihlambulukileyo\x + 11.2-47; Dute. 14.4-20.\x*; lingenzi imiphefumulo yenu inengeke ngezinyamazana loba ngezinyoni loba ngakuphi okuhuquzelayo emhlabathini, engikwehlukanise lani njengokungcolileyo\x + 11.43.\x*.
\v 26 Njalo lizakuba ngcwele kimi, ngoba mina N\nd kosi\nd* ngingcwele\x + 20.7;11.44.\x*; ngilehlukanisile labezizwe ukuze libe ngabami\x + 20.24.\x*.
\p
\v 27 Njalo owesilisa loba owesifazana, abalamadlozi loba abalumbayo, bazabulawa lokubulawa\x + 19.31.\x*, bazabakhanda ngamatshe\x + 20.2.\x*; igazi labo liphezu kwabo\x + 20.9.\x*.
